{"tid":1797852,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"和你subscribe 我宣佈瘋狂訂閱黃絲youtuber!","createTime":"2019-12-25T17:49:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T02:32:04.000Z","uid":240968,"like":35,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"1a273e00dad9400eca997f90ad090bac425b3535","tid":1797852,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T17:49:06.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟園開結成形，但範圍遠遠唔夠紅色資本勁! 我地要自己人撐自己人! 第一步一定係訂閱黃絲youtuber。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地訂閱人數超過1000人先可以開啟收入，放廣告。俾中小型youtuber增加賺錢機會，增加佢地kol既影響力，配合宣佈黃藍地圖，一舉兩得! <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我先舉例! <br />\nray ho <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dyLaAa63qsU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdyLaAa63qsU&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFKtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=cc45019c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dyLaAa63qsU</a> (支持小朋友<br />\n<br />\nEeic 仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Eo5cIamJqOo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEo5cIamJqOo&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFKtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=3a1154a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Eo5cIamJqOo</a> (唱歌好聽)<br />\n<br />\nfatjoe番薯<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ow_A_-PmIVo(見到黃店vlog就擺埋你\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOw_A_-PmIVo%28%E8%A6%8B%E5%88%B0%E9%BB%83%E5%BA%97vlog%E5%B0%B1%E6%93%BA%E5%9F%8B%E4%BD%A0&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFKtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=e6947540\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ow_A_-PmIVo(見到黃店vlog就擺埋你</a><br />\n<br />\n大家一人推介一個，然後入去訂閱，並且留言感謝佢地。最尾希望有高手整一個黃藍youtuber地圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b954b56fa1ab8a5e943c38be997129cf1f8315","tid":1797852,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T17:49:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea899317a0f648b00481f15fe0e02360a17e8cc7","tid":1797852,"uid":93383,"like